{"tid":1154133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"價飆3倍！ 泰柬邊境海關截獲大量「陰道緊縮丸」","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T08:35:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"624f677b85c7a7637a1483c6605c174ce998703d","tid":1154133,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppX2k07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppX2k07.jpg&h=01851a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國執法人員近日在泰柬邊境破獲一藥品走私案件，截獲大量的「陰道緊縮丸」，據報，這些沒有官方標籤又未標明的藥物若走私進入柬埔寨，價格將會高漲3倍。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國媒體報導，泰國沙繳府雅蘭縣泰柬邊境出境檢查口岸10日進行排查時，發現2名推著大量紙箱準備過海關的柬埔寨工人形跡可疑，遂要求開箱檢查，工人見狀立刻丟下物品逃跑，混入遊客群後趁機逃到了柬埔寨。<br />\n<br />\n至於留在泰柬邊境的大量紙箱，一共有10個，裡面裝了4萬4700瓶陰道緊縮丸，瓶內為黃色膠囊。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，這些藥物在泰國售價一瓶約100至200泰銖（約新台幣98至196元），總價值約53.1萬泰銖（約新台幣52萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n泰媒稱，這種藥物在柬埔寨非常暢銷，售價是泰國的3倍。"},{"pid":"4135216bea0b2bad296f3f0b0c3ec100f5d3780b","tid":1154133,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"越暢銷係咪等於越多女做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5ac8a2ae9e263f458e9ae3d80525597d1d9bfa","tid":1154133,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"d鬼鐘意？"},{"pid":"bc0454b1e2589f37f5d1dc3d30a2770e97328047","tid":1154133,"uid":205844,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"香港海關做野未，相信香港冇10億都8億粒要流入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港女闊過西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8938ceb24cbcb